21 n = 3;
(gdb) b 17
Breakpoint 1 at 0x8048481: file main.c, line 17.
(gdb) set follow-fork-mode child
(gdb) r
Starting program: /home/akaedu/a.out This is the parent
[Switching to process 30725] Breakpoint 1, main () at main.c:17
